    {"type":"text","id":"dl_rag_t","x":844,"y":108,"width":222,"height":224,"text":"rag_retrieval\n[Lambda + Haiku + Titan]\n─────────────\nIN: email + intent\nOUT: topK docs + context\n\nPipeline:\n1. HyDE (Haiku generates\n   hypothetical answer)\n2. Titan V2 embed query\n3. BM25 keyword search\n4. RRF fusion\n5. Cross-encoder rerank\n   (Haiku judge)\nOUT: {docs[], scores[]}","originalText":"rag_retrieval\n[Lambda + Haiku + Titan]\n─────────────\nIN: email + intent\nOUT: topK docs + context\n\nPipeline:\n1. HyDE (Haiku generates\n   hypothetical answer)\n2. Titan V2 embed query\n3. BM25 keyword search\n4. RRF fusion\n5. Cross-encoder rerank\n   (Haiku judge)\nOUT: {docs[], scores[]}","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#374151","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":90082,"version":1,"versionNonce":90083,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":"dl_rag","lineHeight":1.25},

